<h1>厦</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">shà</span><span class=alesi>(sha4)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">xià</span><span class=alesi>(xia4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 厦 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 厦</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/big" style="color:black;">big</a> <a href="/dictionary/building" style="color:black;">building</a>, <a href="/dictionary/mansion" style="color:black;">mansion</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 12<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 12 strokes: <a href="/character/就" title="jiu4: just, simply; to come, go to; to approach, near">就</a>, <a href="/character/道" title="dao4: path, road, street; method, way">道</a>, <a href="/character/然" title="ran2: yes, certainly; pledge, promise">然</a>, <a href="/character/最" title="zui4: most, extremely, exceedingly">最</a>, <a href="/character/等" title="">等</a>, <a href="/character/斯" title="si1: this, thus, such; to lop off; emphatic particle">斯</a>, <a href="/character/提" title="ti2: hold in hand; lift in hand">提</a>, <a href="/character/量" title="liang4: measure, quantity, capacity">量</a>, <a href="/character/期" title="qi1: period of time; date; time limit">期</a>, <a href="/character/强" title="qiang2: strong, powerful, energetic">强</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/厂" title="Kangxi radical 27">厂</a>&nbsp;27.10</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/恳" title="ken3: sincere, earnest, cordial">恳</a>, <a href="/character/厘" title="li2: thousandth part of tael">厘</a>, <a href="/character/憾" title="han4: to regret, remorse; dissatisfied">憾</a>, <a href="/character/摔" title="shuai1: fall ground, stumble, trip">摔</a>, <a href="/character/愧" title="kui4: ashamed, conscience-stricken">愧</a>, <a href="/character/鞭" title="bian1: whip; whip; string of firecrackers">鞭</a>, <a href="/character/洒" title="sa3: sprinkle; scatter; pour; to wipe away; to shiver">洒</a>, <a href="/character/窄" title="zhai3: narrow, tight; narrow-minded">窄</a>, <a href="/character/陌" title="mo4: foot path between rice fields">陌</a>, <a href="/character/粘" title="zhan1: viscous, mucous; glutinous">粘</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" ti